google-java-format - Google Java Code Formatter

USAGE:
    google-java-format [files-or-directories...]

DESCRIPTION:
    Format Java source files using Google Java Format.
    Processes files and directories recursively.

ARGUMENTS:
    files-or-directories...
        Java files or directories to format (optional, defaults to all)

CONFIGURATION:
    -conf-dev-java-google-java-format-jdk JDK
        JDK to use for formatting

    -conf-dev-java-google-java-format-options OPTIONS
        Default formatting options

    -conf-dev-google-java-format-jar PATH
        Path to Google Java Format JAR

EXAMPLES:
    google-java-format
    google-java-format src/
    google-java-format File1.java File2.java
